@startuml jlhood_retweet-leaderboard

actor User
participant "API Gateway" as API
participant "GetLeaderboardHandler" as GLH
participant "TweetProcessorHandler" as TPH
participant "TweetProcessor" as TP
participant "Leaderboard" as LB
database "DynamoDB" as DB
participant "aws-serverless-twitter-event-source" as TwitterSource

TwitterSource -> TPH: Send tweet JSON
TPH -> TP: Process tweet
TP -> Tweet: Parse JSON
Tweet --> TP: Return tweet data
TP -> TP: Filter and extract data
TP -> LB: Update leaderboard
LB -> DB: Store/update record

User -> API: GET /leaderboard
API -> GLH: Invoke
GLH -> LB: Get leaderboard data
LB -> DB: Retrieve records
DB --> LB: Return records
LB --> GLH: Return leaderboard data
GLH --> API: Return JSON response
API --> User: Display leaderboard

@enduml